              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "Applications that use UriComponentsBuilder to parse an externally provided URL (e.g. through a query parameter) AND perform validation checks on the host of the parsed URL may be vulnerable to a  open redirect https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/601.html  attack or to a SSRF attack if the URL is used after passing validation checks."
              },
              "help": {
                "markdown": "Applications that use UriComponentsBuilder to parse an externally provided URL (e.g. through a query parameter) AND perform validation checks on the host of the parsed URL may be vulnerable to a  open redirect https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/601.html  attack or to a SSRF attack if the URL is used after passing validation checks.\n\nThis is the same as  CVE-2024-22259 https://spring.io/security/cve-2024-22259  and  CVE-2024-22243 https://spring.io/security/cve-2024-22243 , but with different input.",
                "text": "Applications that use UriComponentsBuilder to parse an externally provided URL (e.g. through a query parameter) AND perform validation checks on the host of the parsed URL may be vulnerable to a  open redirect https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/601.html  attack or to a SSRF attack if the URL is used after passing validation checks.\n\nThis is the same as  CVE-2024-22259 https://spring.io/security/cve-2024-22259  and  CVE-2024-22243 https://spring.io/security/cve-2024-22243 , but with different input."
              },
              "helpUri": "https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/601.html",
