              "help": {
                "markdown": "A specially crafted sequence of HTTP/2 requests sent to Apache Tomcat 10.0.0-M1 to 10.0.0-M5, 9.0.0.M1 to 9.0.35 and 8.5.0 to 8.5.55 could trigger high CPU usage for several seconds. If a sufficient number of such requests were made on concurrent HTTP/2 connections, the server could become unresponsive.",
                "text": "A specially crafted sequence of HTTP/2 requests sent to Apache Tomcat 10.0.0-M1 to 10.0.0-M5, 9.0.0.M1 to 9.0.35 and 8.5.0 to 8.5.55 could trigger high CPU usage for several seconds. If a sufficient number of such requests were made on concurrent HTTP/2 connections, the server could become unresponsive."
              },
              "helpUri": "https://cwe.mitre.org/data/definitions/1035.html",
              "id": "oss_vuln/e38471122c8cc6c9a2dc31c5f9f1c7c2",
              "name": "Pkg:maven/Org.apache.tomcat.embed/Tomcat-Embed-Core@8.5.11",
